title: How to Paint: 'Red Era' Warhammer Fantasy Orcs & Goblins
description:
In celebration of 40 years of Warhammer, we have a painting guide to show you how to paint 'Red Era' Warhammer Fantasy Orcs & Goblins!      

If you're new to painting - check out our Citadel Colour Painting Essentials videos to learn all about it: http://warhammer.me/3Vkojs6
